OL,3,CSenedd Election 2026: Leaders face
OL,4,Ceach other in ITV Cymru Wales debate
OL,6,FWith the Senedd Election less than
OL,7,Fthree weeks away, the leaders of
OL,8,FWales' six larger political parties
OL,9,Fwill be going head-to-head in ITV
OL,10,FCymru Wales' election special
OL,11,Fprogramme: 'Wales Decides 2026 - The
OL,12,FDebate'.
OL,14,FPresented by Adrian Masters, it will
OL,15,Fsee the leaders of Wales' Six Major
OL,16,Fparties battling it out on a live
OL,17,Fbroadcast in the Senedd, hoping to
OL,18,Fpersuade the people of Wales to vote
OL,19,Ffor them in the Senedd Election on
OL,20,FThursday 7 May.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
