OL,3,CSenedd Election 2026: Leaders face
OL,4,Ceach other in ITV Cymru Wales debate
OL,6,FMembers of the public have been
OL,7,Fgetting involved by submitting their
OL,8,Fquestions, which will be given to the
OL,9,Fleaders to answer during the debate.
OL,11,FThe debate will tackle issues shaping
OL,12,Feveryday life across the country, from
OL,13,Fthe future of healthcare to the
OL,14,Fongoing cost-of-living pressures.
OL,16,FThe special programme will air at 8-
OL,17,F10pm on Sunday 19 April.
OL,19,FThe leaders taking part in the debate:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
