OL,3,CSenedd Election 2026: Leaders face
OL,4,Ceach other in ITV Cymru Wales debate
OL,6,FThe programme will be broadcast live
OL,7,Ffrom the the Senedd. Each leader will
OL,8,Fstand at an individual lectern
OL,9,Fthroughout the debate.
OL,11,FIt will be divided into eight parts
OL,12,Fwith seven commercial breaks. Seven
OL,13,Fsegments will focus on the debate,
OL,14,Fwith each debate topic lasting
OL,15,Fapproximately 12 minutes.
OL,17,FThe final section of the programme
OL,18,Fwill be dedicated to analysis from a
OL,19,Fpanel.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
