OL,3,CSenedd Election 2026: Leaders face
OL,4,Ceach other in ITV Cymru Wales debate
OL,6,FThere will be no opening statements.
OL,7,FEach candidate will instead deliver a
OL,8,Fclosing statement of up to 30 seconds.
OL,10,FThe full debate programme will air
OL,11,Flive on ITV Cymru Wales and will be
OL,12,Favailable on ITVX as well as Youtube.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
